{"tid":1445111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"獨立思考好重要","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:00:52.000Z","uid":304595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fdea1e17047e5c64299b2736a425485e899111b4","tid":1445111,"uid":304595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:55:31.000Z","msg":"只係想同所有手足講<br />\n無論前線又好 支援又好 冷氣軍事都好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">保持獨立思考 真係好重要</span><br />\n<br />\n唔洗屌我p牌同到底冇上過前線<br />\n<br />\n無論面對任何事 都會有人帶風向 都會有人陰鳩你<br />\n進定退 自己決定<br />\n思考完就根據自己既意志去做<br />\n<br />\n其實講咁多只係想話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好入北角呀大家</span></span>"},{"pid":"a9e8e1bf9cefa0b328ecffd46f22fe782d946546","tid":1445111,"uid":275074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"北角地鐵有狗守門口"}]}